Bitcoin-24.com is the biggest bitcoin exchange in Europe and is only surpassed by MtGox in terms of EURO volume.
They offer instant registration and trading and impose no restrictions and limits on withdrawals and deposits.
EUROs can be deposited instantly by credit card and bank transfer. You can also trade in USD, which can be added by credit card, bank wire and MtGox Code. Bitcoin-24.com is not charging any fees for Bitcoin transactions, which only need 3 confirmations to reach Bitcoin-24.com.

##Deposits

###USD

* Bank wire transfer (International)
* Credit card (instant through LiqPay)
* [[Redeemable_code]] ([[MtGox]], VouchX) (fee applies)

###EUR

* SEPA/Bank wire
* Sofort (instant within the EU)
* Credit card (instant through LiqPay)
* Redeemable Code (MtGox, VouchX) (fee applies)
* GIROPay

###GBP

* Bank wire transfer (International) [to EUR](Converts)

###PLN

* Bank wire transfer (International) [to EUR](Converts)

###BTC

* Bitcoins may be deposited free of charge.

##Withdrawals

###USD

* ([[Skrill (Moneybookers)|Skrill]])
* Bank wire transfer (International)

###EUR

* SEPA wire
* Cash (via DHL) (fee applies)

###BTC

* A 0.0005 BTC transaction fee applies for each withdrawal of bitcoins.

##History

* The exchange was first live in May, 2012.

